{"tid":1422850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇住屋企變黃","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:42:32.000Z","uid":49836,"like":116,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"662272c08e47c8a0c8d8cb3c758fb5531268cf50","tid":1422850,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:08:54.000Z","msg":"我幾年前問家母 有無登記做選民 <br />\n佢答我 無啊 政治既野邊識咁多<br />\n係當年雨革我啊媽都係偏向中立 啊爸就淺黃<br />\n<br />\n直到69至今 每次遊行都有出動 幾熱都行足全程 <br />\n屋企無睇cctvb好耐 仲會識上連登 睇蘋果立場 成日同我講好擔心啲後生仔 遊行仲會行行下 指住啲狗當面屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成場運動睇住屋企人向深黃邁進 真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最感動係前幾日講講下 啊媽同我講希望佢地張選票有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗都無諗過 幾年後 我媽教返我咩叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公民責任</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚自豪出生於一個咁理智既家庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSb7wcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSb7wcb.png&h=03957370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zvMjniR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzvMjniR.png&h=3e30f964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a17174720f563cd59af09f7e2084ca5c79cc84e6","tid":1422850,"uid":49836,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"文宣要加油 真係會感化到好多中立既人 我媽就係例子"},{"pid":"c07dd73cafcdcabc77e7e58e1c0ae8e3069ce552","tid":1422850,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hk